div.p: > Hello, I'm Chad, a frontend engineer from Covington, Louisiana.
> I’ve always had a strong passion for the web. Shortly after I was given my first computer, I grew interested in web development.
> I'm constantly furthering my skills to keep up with the ever changing demand the web has.
> I've always enjoyed the feeling of accomplishment when programming, and I take pride in writing clean, maintainable, and efficient code.
